  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Create a model for harmonious living in Costa Rica</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In partnership with the National University of Costa Rica (UNA), IBREA Foundation will create a social model for peaceful living, through working with two rural areas in Heredia Costa Rica. Through providing brain-based holistic education to a focal group in each community, IBREA aims to establish the foundation for that process. Participants will go through a process of healing their body&amp;mind to unleash their natural tendency for harmonious living &amp; take action to make it a reality.</narrative>
  </description>
